    "This multinational study that was conducted among academics and students in Brazil, India, Japan, UK, and USA, regarding their perspectives on ChatGPT, indicated that a majority of students intend to use ChatGPT for assignment support and anticipate that their peers would endorse its usage, implying a potential shift towards ChatGPT use becoming a standard practice among university students 60.",
    "Recently, Strzelecki meticulously delineated the factors behind adoption of ChatGPT among Polish state university students 61.",
